Compilation Instructions
------------------------

To compile both serial and parallel versions:

    make

This generates two executables:

    serial_ocean
    omp_ocean


To remove executables:

    make clean


Running Instructions
--------------------

1. Serial Version

Usage:

    ./serial_ocean -d <dimension> -t <timesteps>

Example:

    ./serial_ocean -d 258 -t 64


2. Parallel Version

Usage:

    ./omp_ocean -d <dimension> -t <timesteps> -n <threads>

Example:

    ./omp_ocean -d 258 -t 64 -n 8


Test Parameters
---------------

The following parameters were used for testing:

1. Grid Dimension (<dim>)

    [18, 66, 258, 1026, 4098]

These correspond to:
    (2^n) + 2
where n = [4, 6, 8, 10, 12]

2. Timesteps (<timesteps>)

    [4, 16, 64, 256]

3. Number of Threads (<threads>)

    [1, 2, 4, 8, 16, 32, 64]
